  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2 40 \u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u00a0 \u0baa\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "40 new buses to transport school students in service from tomorrow",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The National Transport Commission has informed that 40 new buses will be put into service from tomorrow (01) to transport school students.",
        "Nilan Miranda, Director General of the National Transport Commission, said that these buses will be added to the service in addition to the existing \"Sisu Seria\" buses.",
        "According to this, under the new service, students will be transported subject to normal bus fare."
      ],
